message.body: Yeah sorry man I sent that to you by accident!! How's life with you?
Life is great! How about with you?
Im thinking bout moving back to philly in the fall
I'm good man. Still holding it down in west philly. Where are you these days?
Im in burlington vt still, and love it but im ready for a bit bigger of a city and miss philly
Yeah I hear ya man. I'm trying to figure out if I wanna stay or go myself. Let me know the next time you're in philly and let's meet up!
